leet Code 122 Buy and Sell Stock 2
-----------------------------------

Solution - Buy whenever we see a profit is on next day, we are adding up all the ups in price, thus max profit.

class Solution {
    public int maxProfit(int[] prices) {
        int money=0,currPrice,prevPrice;
        
        for(int i =1; i< prices.length;i++){
            currPrice = prices[i];
            prevPrice = prices[i-1];
            if(currPrice>prevPrice){
                money+=currPrice-prevPrice;
            }
        }
        return money;
    }
}
